<p>By cultivating a traditional garden and a community garden, Jessica had the vision to help students understand the benefits of a garden, and to be able to use the harvests. She wished to organize traditional activities, either related to crafting, such as the creation of corn puppets with the leaves of the corn; or to eating, for example cooking workshops or a corn tasting.</p>
